				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/C%E1%BA%A3m-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-0TpDWmGOuKAqTEJKykNMag">Cảm sự - 感事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/D%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%99-Ki%E1%BA%BFn-Giang-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh/poem-3aWMLriyMgI7j1hR1cprWg">Dạ độ Kiến Giang ngẫu thành - 夜渡建江偶成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/S%C6%A1n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Sơn hành - 山行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Lang-S%C4%A9-Nguy%C3%AAn/Th%C3%ADnh-l%C3%A2n-gia-xuy-sinh/poem-Zy2ZxgPzxI2xVckA9k8Pkg">Thính lân gia xuy sinh - 聽鄰家吹笙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Lang-S%C4%A9-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-NB7nk8Nge4yBjrV5IbQvgA">Lang Sĩ Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Th%C6%B0-Thi%C3%AAn-Tr%C3%BAc-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-5ex8_B5MYEkb33vXdIULiQ">Thư Thiên Trúc tự - 書天竺寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/Tr%C3%AC-gi%E1%BB%9Bi-ki%C3%AAm-nh%E1%BA%ABn-nh%E1%BB%A5c/poem-UVeKVCaO6_GsgCNIG1Y6Xg">Trì giới kiêm nhẫn nhục - 持戒兼忍辱</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C3%A2n/poem-up9Vx1UZSnrd09bAq2TgLQ">Vân - 雲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%90%C3%A0o/V%E1%BB%8Dng-xu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-r1_LASbnem2Qdupk_lzO3Q">Vọng xuân từ kỳ 1 - 春望詞其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%90%C3%A0o/author-YFc6G7OeOIRiUPVl88lFdA">Tiết Đào</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-B%C3%A2n/Xu%C3%A2n-m%E1%BB%99/poem-iEEfo6yR1E5NAirJPmvr4A">Xuân mộ - 春暮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-B%C3%A2n/author-UAF7vcnrHUZGBBSnb3ZD9Q">Tào Bân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-04/poem-82wx8VAIFRM62TxBEXxf4Q">Xuân nhật tuyệt cú thập thủ kỳ 04 - 春日絕句十首其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
